Title: Relates to the administration of reversible progestin-only contraceptive injections
Summary: Relates to the administration of reversible progestin-only contraceptive injections; provides that no pharmacist shall administer reversible progestin-only contraceptive injections without receiving training satisfactory to the commissioner of education and the commissioner of health.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to the administration of reversible progestin-only contraceptive injections
